{"tid":1734434,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"「社工之恥」社署穩工 vs 非政府社工","createTime":"2019-11-18T10:33:16.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-18T13:19:13.000Z","uid":186,"like":1,"dislike":16,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"edd2c7c88afe14743c6d61e35d17c3b517f264fb","tid":1734434,"uid":186,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T10:33:16.000Z","msg":"呢場運動五個月以來有幾多非政府外展嘅社工一直陪着學生做唔同嘅支援<br />\n有幾多社工上身苦苦同班仔建立關係信任<br />\n<br />\n你班社署社工有無係工作上幫過咩忙<br />\n平時公務員上身 社工精神唔見<br />\n我都唔屌你<br />\n依家你班仆街 <br />\n名正言順去做維穩機器<br />\n竟然幫班popo 捉仔<br />\n<br />\n唔好叫社工啦 叫穩工啦<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/47jside.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F47jside.jpg&h=8c1d7556&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"a978159a1685a0661037506cdae11a4500bc0b2b","tid":1734434,"uid":186,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T10:33:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7ff019c21017973afe5762177f283ba873bb0ef6","tid":1734434,"uid":186,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T10:34:00.000Z","msg":"維穩工作主任 vs 社會工作員"},{"pid":"2ea55a1d5d3c6e72d13777d9b6a1a705732ce5d1","tid":1734434,"uid":186,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T10:34:37.000Z","msg":"抗爭唔預你 <br />\n係到倒社工個名米"},{"pid":"45b34890be62f92ddd59a7171ebc60a08be0ab41","tid":1734434,"uid":186,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T10:34:50.000Z","msg":"報警撚<br />\n捉仔撚"},{"pid":"4ea1af76cdbf1b3b88f97a59732e5dc54f3a321c","tid":1734434,"uid":186,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T10:35:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" cl